{
  "stem": "26142.18",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The, the, the chicken coops, they cleared it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had barracks where the German SS was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were clear barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They cleared that up, and they put in beds-- in huge rooms, beds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they started to take out the sick and, and, and tried to, to select them out and see what they can do with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And don't forget, the war was still going on a few days, a week.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had-- the military, the military had the, the portable x-ray machines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were x-raying people in, in the beds.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and they were starting to take, to take stock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left Dachau the ninth of June, to the sanatorium Gauting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first week or two, there were 200 people still dying daily in Dachau, dying from, from, from, from, from the diseases.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I left in June the ninth, which was already exactly a month after the war, there were still 50 people dying every day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we, in that-- we talked about, about experiments-- in that room where I was, there were two people from Yugoslavia that they conducted experiments on them to know how, how much freezing water the human body is capable of standing.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, those two people were like one raw, raw piece of flesh.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They, both of them died a few, a few days after, after.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was already after liberation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's the only thing that I came, came across with, with medical.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I should say-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started saying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I keep forgetting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I weighed 67 pounds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was sick, sick, skin and bone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't able to turn around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how weak I was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the, when the American doctor first came, and I was reading his mind.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was looking at him.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
